---
title: Sausage and Pepper Hoagies with Marinara and Roasted Potatoes
description: This ballpark classic is perfect for baseball season! All the components are cooked in the same pan for maximum flavour, leaving you with almost no clean-up so you’ll be able to sit back and enjoy the game.
